13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Isitish kalkulyatori O'zbekistonda turli usullarda uy-joyni isitish narxini hisoblaydi: markaziy isitish, gaz qozoni, elektr isitgich, issiqlik pompasi. O'zbekistonda isitish mavsumi oktyabrdan martgacha davom etadi (taxminan 180 kun), qishda o'rtacha harorat Toshkentda 0-5°C, Qoraqalpog'istonda −10°C gacha tushadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2025-2026 mavsumi uchun isitish narxi (Toshkentda 60 m² kvartira): markaziy isitish — 1 800 000-2 500 000 so'm (normativ bo'yicha to'lov ~420 000 so'm/oy); individual gaz qozoni — 2 500 000-4 500 000 so'm (oyiga 300-500 m³ gaz sarfi, tarif ~1 000 so'm/m³); elektr isitgichlar — 4 000 000-7 000 000 so'm (oyiga 2 000-3 500 kVt·soat sarfi, tarif ~600 so'm/kVt·soat)."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Xususiy uy (100 m²) uchun xarajatlar ancha yuqori: gaz qozoni — izolyatsiya va issiqlik yo'qotishlariga qarab mavsumiga 5 000 000-10 000 000 so'm. Ko'mir bilan isitish (qishloq joylarda keng tarqalgan): 3 000 000-6 000 000 so'm (3-5 tonna ko'mir sarfi, narxi ~1 200 000 so'm/tonna). Issiqlik pompasi — boshlang'ich investitsiya $3 000-5 000 dan, lekin foydalanish elektrdan 60-70% arzon."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Uyni izolyatsiya qilish — isitish xarajatlarini kamaytirishning eng samarali usuli. Eski yog'och derazalarni steklopaketlarga almashtirish 20-30% issiqlikni tejaydi (narxi derazasiga 3 000 000 so'mdan). Fasadni penoplast bilan izolyatsiya qilish — 120 000 so'm/m² dan, 30-40% issiqlik tejash. Tomni izolyatsiya qilish — 15-20% tejash. Jami izolyatsiyaga sarmoyalar 2-3 isitish mavsumida qoplanadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Saytimizda isitish kalkulyatori xona maydonini, bino turini (kvartira, xususiy uy), isitish usulini, O'zbekiston hududini va izolyatsiya darajasini hisobga oladi. Parametrlarni kiriting — oylik va butun mavsumga narx hisobini olasiz. Bu optimal isitish usulini tanlash va qishki davrga oilaviy byudjetni rejalashtirishga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"Elektr energiya tariflari (so'm/kVt·s)"}],"$L18","$L19"]}]}],"$L1a","$L1b"]]}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]
